- 我就知道会这样 - 什么?
- I knew this was gonna happen. - What?

42
00:07:36,391 --> 00:07:39,890
- 没事 - 你知道会发生什么事?
- Nothing. - What did you know was going to happen?

43
00:07:39,978 --> 00:07:41,887
