and wait for that neighbour with the enormous head to get drunk and fall down.

54
00:08:10,214 --> 00:08:13,334
他得了水脑症 你不应该这样取笑他
He's a hydrocephalic. I don't think that you should make fun of him.

55
00:08:13,426 --> 00:08:15,833
