<i>Smoke an occasional cigar... outside.</i>

61
00:08:30,108 --> 00:08:33,192
我会修理后院的烤肉架
I'll fix the barbecue in the backyard. I'll do that.

62
00:08:33,278 --> 00:08:37,027
卡罗 这正是我想要的
This is what I need, Carol. I need... this.

63
00:08:37,115 --> 00:08:41,113
等着瞧 一周之后我就会脱胎换骨
And at the end of the week, I'll be a brand new human being.

64
00:08:41,203 --> 00:08:43,444
反正这是你的休假
It's your vacation.

65
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:46,505
【文森】

