<i>Hey, hi, Ray. Are you guys eatin' in there?</i>

69
00:09:35,546 --> 00:09:38,500
你知道苏珊对她的喂鸟器很讲究挑剔
You know how Suzette is about her bird feeder.

70
00:09:38,590 --> 00:09:40,666
这些乌鸦不知道从哪里跑出来
These crows start showing up out of nowhere.

71
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:42,668
她一直念着要我把它们赶走
She's all over my back to get rid of 'em.

72
00:09:42,761 --> 00:09:45,003
她说 乌鸦太大了 用不了喂食器
"The crows are too big for the bird feeder," she says.

73
00:09:45,097 --> 00:09:47,670
- 我不记得以前看过乌鸦 - 坏得很
- I don't remember seeing crows around before. - Oh, big bastards too.

74
00:09:47,766 --> 00:09:50,173
所以我才拿着枪 准备射个几只
That's why I got the gun. I'm gonna pop a few.

75
00:09:50,268 --> 00:09:53,185
你怎么不跟苏珊去她妈妈家?
Why didn't you go with Suzette to her mother's?

76
00:09:53,271 --> 00:09:57,518
嘿 我在这里这里吃饭 你能想像我和她们俩单独相处一星期吗?
Hey, I'm eating here. Can you imagine me and the two of them alone for a week?

77
00:09:57,608 --> 00:09:59,684
我宁愿嚼碎玻璃
I'd rather chew broken glass.

78
00:09:59,777 --> 00:10:04,190
这是单身汉的黄金假期啊
Uh-uh, this is gonna be a big week for the bachelor kid.

79
00:10:04,282 --> 00:10:06,274
文森
<i>Vince.</i>

80
00:10:06,367 --> 00:10:08,858
文森
<i>Vince.</i>

81
00:10:08,953 --> 00:10:10,909
雷 你怎么没去上班?
How come you're not at work, Ray?

82
00:10:10,996 --> 00:10:14,281
- 我请了一星期的假 - 一星期的休假?
- I took the week off. - A week off?

83
00:10:14,374 --> 00:10:16,865
真好 你们打算去湖边吗?
That's great. Are you guys going to the lake or something?

84
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:19,202
- 不 后院 - 后院?
- No, the backyard. - Backyard?

85
00:10:19,296 --> 00:10:21,703
我只想待在家里休息
I just want to hang around the house and relax.

86
00:10:21,798 --> 00:10:25,713
休息? 看看你们隔壁的怪胎 祝你好运
Relax? Good luck with those maniacs you got living next door.

87
00:10:25,802 --> 00:10:28,376
- 你有见过柯罗佩一家人吗? - 没有
- Have you met the Klopeks yet? - No.

88
00:10:28,472 --> 00:10:31,222
我没见过 这条街上没人见过
No, I haven't. Nobody on the block has.

89
00:10:31,307 --> 00:10:35,719
可是我和卖房子给他们的那个女经纪人谈过
But I did talk to the real estate broad that sold them the place.

90
00:10:35,811 --> 00:10:39,643
据说他们上一栋房子被烧了
Apparently, their last house only burnt to the ground.

91
00:10:39,732 --> 00:10:42,223
- 真的吗? - 是啊
- Really? - Yep.

92
00:10:42,318 --> 00:10:46,861
燃烧的恐怖地狱
A hideous, raging inferno.

93
00:10:48,115 --> 00:10:50,071
