Neighbours from hell.

94
00:10:52,327 --> 00:10:54,236
也许吧
Maybe.

95
00:10:54,329 --> 00:10:58,077
不论如何 我很庆幸我不住在他们隔壁
Whatever it is, I'm glad I'm not the one who lives right next door.

96
00:10:58,166 --> 00:11:02,911
来吧 让我们面对现实 柯罗佩一家很古怪
Come on, let's face it. These Klopeks are strange.

97
00:11:03,004 --> 00:11:05,165
从他们搬来以后我就一直在观察
I've been watching that house ever since they moved in.

98
00:11:05,173 --> 00:11:07,925
没人进来 没人出去
No one goes in. No one comes out.

99
00:11:08,009 --> 00:11:10,416
没有访客 没有送货
No visitors. No deliveries.

100
00:11:10,511 --> 00:11:12,468
你觉得他们都吃什么?
What do you think they're eatin', Ray?

101
00:11:14,431 --> 00:11:17,432
也许这些人只想独来独往
Well, maybe these people just want to keep to themselves, Art.

102
00:11:17,518 --> 00:11:19,594
还记得以前住在隔壁的纳普斯家吗?
Remember when the Knapps lived next door?

103
00:11:19,686 --> 00:11:21,928
