These Klopeks... We don't even know how many of them there are.

110
00:11:38,871 --> 00:11:40,947
一共有三人
<i>There are three of them.</i>

111
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:43,875
只有晚上才会出来
They only come out at night.

112
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:46,451
