Oh, Ricky Butler says.

114
00:11:48,131 --> 00:11:51,545
上星期我拿着望远镜爬上屋顶
Last week when I was up on the roof with my telescope...

115
00:11:51,633 --> 00:11:53,875
看到他们在自己的后院
I saw them in their backyard.

116
00:11:53,969 --> 00:11:57,753
