嘿 伦斯菲太太
<i>Hey, Mrs Rumsfield.</i>

130
00:12:54,735 --> 00:12:57,308
今天早上没有晒黑线
No tan lines this morning.

131
00:12:57,404 --> 00:13:01,272
很俏
<i>Looks nice.</i>

132
