- 要拿它们盖东西吗? - 应该会吧
- You gonna build something with those? - I think so. Probably

145
00:13:46,118 --> 00:13:48,822
球赛什么时候开始?
Hey, what time does the ball game go on?

146
00:13:48,912 --> 00:13:51,069
大概一点吧
I think it's at about 1:00.

147
00:13:51,163 --> 00:13:53,452
你想去小吃店买个牛肉三明治吗?
<i>You want to go down to the deli and get one of those beef sandwiches?</i>

148
00:13:53,541 --> 00:14:00,504
不想 我要去买车库门的电动开关来装
<i>No. I'm thinking of getting one of those electric garage door openers And installing 

