那是什么?
What is it?

153
00:14:22,735 --> 00:14:25,191
是我的邻居
It's my neighbour.

154
00:14:26,406 --> 00:14:31,826
一个匈奴人从洞穴走出来了
Hey, one of the Huns came out of the cave.

155
00:15:05,943 --> 00:15:08,730
去打声招呼吧
Why don't you go say hi?

156
00:15:10,155 --> 00:15:12,397
是呀 何不呢?
Well, yeah, I guess I could.

157
00:15:12,491 --> 00:15:15,408
这个时机最恰好
This would be the perfect time.

158
00:15:15,494 --> 00:15:18,827
如果你去和他搭讪 我们就能知道他是什么德行了 去吧
If you go talk to him, we could see what he's like. Go.

159
00:15:18,914 --> 00:15:21,239
你也可以跟他打招呼啊
You could say hi to him too.

160
00:15:21,333 --> 00:15:23,733
- 可是他是你的邻居 - 他也是你的邻居
- But he's your neighbour. - No, he's your neighbour as well.

161
00:15:23,794 --> 00:15:26,082
可是你的房子和他交界
But you share a property line with him.

162
00:15:26,171 --> 00:15:28,744
我们都在同一条街上 所以你也可以去
We're all on the same block, so you could go too.

163
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:31,924
我们都在同一个小镇 可是你在他隔壁
We're all in the same town, but you're next to him.

164
00:15:32,009 --> 00:15:34,251
如果他要借东西 他会找你
<i>If he was gonna borrow anything, he'd come over to your place.</i>

165
00:15:34,345 --> 00:15:36,966
