- 只是打个比方 - 是笑话 他在开玩笑
- It's just a figure of speech. - It's a joke. He's kiddin' around.

824
01:07:12,955 --> 01:07:15,197
是瓦特的假发
<i>Oh, it's Walter's rug.</i>

825
01:07:15,291 --> 01:07:18,161
你拿到老头的假发了 不得了
<i>You got an old guy's wig. Big deal.</i>

826
01:07:18,252 --> 01:07:21,206
你整天都把它塞在裤子里吗?
You've had that in your trousers all day?

827
01:07:21,297 --> 01:07:26,540
你昨天在瓦特家找到之后
After you found this in Walter's house yesterday...

828
01:07:26,636 --> 01:07:31,047
我把它塞回信箱里了
I slipped it back in through the mail slot.

829
01:07:31,139 --> 01:07:34,888
这一次是从哪里来的?
Where did you get it this time?

830
01:07:37,812 --> 01:07:39,888
柯罗佩家? 哇赛
Klopeks? Wow.

831
01:07:39,981 --> 01:07:42,733
狗从地下室冲出来的时候
After the dog came up out of the basement.

832
01:07:42,817 --> 01:07:44,893
我发现它塞在一堆杂志中间
I found it wedged between a bunch of magazines...

833
01:07:44,986 --> 01:07:48,236
杂志都是寄给瓦特的
all of which were addressed to Walter.

834
01:07:48,323 --> 01:07:51,905
那意思就是说...
Then that means that...

835
01:07:51,992 --> 01:07:56,903
柯罗佩潜回瓦特家里...
Klopeks went back inside Walter's house...

836
01:07:56,997 --> 01:07:59,405
拿到假发
and got the hair.

837
01:08:04,171 --> 01:08:07,089
士兵 我们该怎么办?
What do we do now, soldier?

838
01:08:07,174 --> 01:08:10,589
你听到他们说明天要出们
You heard them say they were going away tomorrow.

839
01:08:10,677 --> 01 :08:12,005


840
01:08:12,095 --> 01:08:14,420
早上等车子一开走...
As soon as that car leaves in the morning...

841
01:08:14,514 --> 01:08:19,508
我就要跳过篱笆 找不到尸体誓不回来
I'm going over the fence and I'm not comin' back 'til I find a dead body.

842
01:08:21,187 --> 01:08:25,600
没有人能干掉我街上的老人还逍遥法外
Nobody knocks off an old man in my neighbourhood and gets away with it.

843
01:09:21,411 --> 01:09:26,488
各位 我们全副警戒
Gentlemen, we are on alert.

844
01:09:26,583 --> 01:09:28,492
亲爱的 你知道可以做什么吗?
Honey, you know what you could do?

845
01:09:28,585 --> 01:09:32,202
去园艺中心买些石板铺在走道上
Go get those flag stones at the garden centre and put them along the walk.

846
01:09:32,296 --> 01:09:34,170
那是一件好差事
Yeah, that'd be a nice project.

847
01:09:34,256 --> 01:09:37,839
可是我今天要和阿特打一个半小时的四人二球赛
I've got a foursome lined up with Art today in an hour and a half though.

848
01:09:37,926 --> 01:09:40,678
我又不是说马上 你讨厌高尔夫的
I didn't mean right now. You hate golf.

849
01:09:40,763 --> 01:09:43,847
我在休假 我只想出去透透气
Well, it's my vacation. I just wanted to get out of the house.

850
01:09:43,932 --> 01:09:46,009
被我烦了一星期 你应该也想出去兜兜风
I would think, after the week I put you through, you'd want to too.

851
01:09:46,101 --> 01:09:49,849
为什么我觉得你想摆脱我?
Why do I get the impression you're trying to get rid of me?

852
01:09:49,937 --> 01:09:53,271
我要出去一整天 这是你去拜访艾芙琳的好机会
I'm gonna be gone all day. It'd be a good time for you to go see Evelyn.

853
01:09:53,358 --> 01:09:55,516
跟表弟妹好好玩
And you have a good time with the cousins.

854
01:09:55,610 --> 01:09:59,275
我讨厌他们 鲁迪是白痴 黛安好臭
I hate them, Dad. Rudy is a moron, and Diane smells.

855
01:09:59,364 --> 01:10:01,855
周末愉快
Have a nice weekend.

856
01:10:03,284 --> 01:10:06,036
回头见
I'll see you later.

857
01:10:09,457 --> 01:10:11,864
卡罗 看我的新高尔夫手套
<i>Hey, Carol, see my new golf glove?</i>

858
01:10:11,959 --> 01:10:14,035
这样我打高尔夫就不会起水泡了
I got it so I don't get blisters playing golf.

859
01:10:14,127 --> 01:10:16,369
我们真的要大打特打
We're gonna be playing that much golf. Really.

860
01:10:17,631 --> 01:10:19,873
前面当心
Fore!

861
01:10:19,967 --> 01:10:22,043
你认为她相信吗?
Think she bought it?

862
01:10:32,770 --> 01:10:36,637
史帝夫 怎么样?
Yo, Steve-man. What's the haps, dude?

863
01:10:36,732 --> 01:10:39,899
你今天一定要过来 保证精彩
You gotta come down here today. It's gonna be live.

864
01:10:39,986 --> 01:10:42,062
不 你一定要来
No, you've got to.

865
01:10:42,154 --> 01:10:45,404
有大事要发生 我不能告诉你
Something's about to happen. I can't tell you.

866
01:10:51,830 --> 01:10:53,739
你知道你在干什么吗 阿特?
Are you sure you know what you're doing, Art?

867
01:10:53,832 --> 01:10:55,908
那些电线里面都是电
There's a lot of juice going through those wires.

868
01:10:56,001 --> 01:10:58,077
要是碰错了 你就烤熟了
You hit the wrong one, you're a Post Toastie.

869
01:10:58,169 --> 01:11:00,328
电力是我的朋友
Electricity is our friend.

870
01:11:00,422 --> 01:11:02,382
何况 我们要摘掉他们的警铃
Besides, we wanna take out their alarms, don't we?

871
01:11:02,424 --> 01:11:06,421
也许我们可以避开篱笆另外找条路
I was thinking we could bypass the fence altogether and find another way in.

872
01:11:06,511 --> 01:11:08,919
没有人知道他们有多少警铃
No one knows how many trip alarms they have in there.

873
01:11:09,014 --> 01:11:12,595
不 我只要喀擦一声就可以全部摆平
No, I can take out everything they've got with one clip of the snips.

874
01:11:12,683 --> 01:11:14,759
- 是吧 队长? - 肯定
- Right, Captain? - Affirmative.

875
01:11:17,521 --> 01:11:19,597
警铃模式
Siren mode.

876
01:11:19,690 --> 01:11:22,607
很酷吧?
Pretty neat, eh?

877
01:11:22,693 --> 01:11:25,101
我可以连接所有警铃频道
I can raise all the police channels...

878
01:11:25,195 --> 01:11:28,362
和电力公司频道
and the power company channels on this baby.

879
01:11:28,449 --> 01:11:30,606
- 阿特 小心点 - 没问题的 雷 
<i>- Be careful up there, Art. - It's okay, Ray.</i>

880
01:11:30,700 --> 01:11:33,784
我们得赶紧行动才行 我们正在耗时间
We gotta get going though. We're burning daylight here.

881
01:11:36,873 --> 01:11:40,787
我们过去后 应该从哪里挖起?
Hey, where should we start diggin' once we get over there?

882
01:11:40,877 --> 01:11:44,791
从后院开始 然后检查地下室
We start in the backyard, then check the basement.

883
01:11:44,881 --> 01:11:47,004
上面小心点 慢慢来
Be careful up there. Go slow, huh?

884
01:11:47,091 --> 01:11:50,340
安全是我的中间名
Hey, safety is my middle name.

885
01:11:51,386 --> 01:11:54,304
我以为他的中间名是路易
I thought his middle name was Louis.

886
01:11:55,891 --> 01:11:58,464
你确定你没问题吗?
<i>Are you sure you're all right up there?</i>

887
01:11:58,560 --> 01:12:00,517
他知道自己在干麻吗?
I don't know that he knows what he's doing.

888
01:12:00,604 --> 01:12:04,981
- 那你为什么不上去? - 太高了
- Well, why didn't you go up there? - It's very high.

889
01:12:13,824 --> 01:12:17,407
天哪!
Oh, Jesus!

890
01:12:19,413 --> 01:12:22,782
老天 快用那玩意叫救护车
Jesus Christ! Get an ambulance on that thing!

891
01:12:25,711 --> 01:12:28,629
我没事
I'm okay. I'm all right.

893
01:12:32,842 --> 01:12:34,752
我触电了 可是没事
I took a jolt, but I'm okay.

894
01:12:34,844 --> 01:12:36,754
你能站起来吗? 
Can you stand up? 

895
01:12:36,846 --> 01:12:40,262
- 试试这个 - 好多了
- Try one of these. - Oh, yeah, that's better.

896
01:12:40,350 --> 01:12:42,758
老天
No, no, no. Jesus.

897
01:12:42,852 --> 01:12:46,518
看我的手指
Look at my fingers.

898
01:12:46,606 --> 01:12:50,603
指甲都变黑了
My fingernails are black.

899
01:12:50,693 --> 01:12:53,362
- 我补的牙好热 - 看看这
- My fillings are hot. - Hey, look at this.

900
01:12:53,445 --> 01:12:57,194
他还真切对了线路 警铃没响
The man actually hit the right wire. There's no alarm.

901
01:12:57,283 --> 01:13:00,865
- 干得好 - 恭喜
- Hey, good work. - Congratulations

902
01:13:00,953 --> 01:13:04,536
- 我要去建立通讯基地了 祝一切顺利 - 好的
- I'm gonna set up a communications base. - You got it.

903
01:13:04,623 --> 01:13:08,288
拿去 你需要这个
Here, you're gonna need this.

904
01:13:32,899 --> 01:13:35,355
伦斯菲 老兄
Hey, hey, hey, Rumsfield! Dude!

905
01:13:35,444 --> 01:13:37,483
你拿着枪做什么?
What are you doing with the gun?

906
01:13:37,571 --> 01:13:40,406
闭上你的狗嘴 漆你他妈的房子
Just shut up and paint your goddam house!

907
01:13:40,490 --> 01:13:44,322
哇赛 好
Whoa! Fine.

908
01:13:49,708 --> 01:13:53,076
特遣部队一号 这是鹰眼
Task Force One, this is Eagle Eye.

909
01:13:53,169 --> 01:13:56,538
一切安全
You are all clear.

910
01:13:58,049 --> 01:14:00,337
收到了 鹰眼 我们正要跨过去
Roger, Eagle Eye. We're going over.

911
01:14:00,426 --> 01:14:05,800
收到了 红罗浮 让雷跨过去
Roger. Red rover, red rover, let Ray go over.

912
01:14:08,017 --> 01:14:12,345
很好 现在 红罗浮 让阿特跨过去
Good. Now, red rover, red rover, let Art go on over.

913
01:14:16,733 --> 01:14:19,141
好极了 结束
That's great. Over.

914
01:14:25,367 --> 01:14:28,237
天气变得好热
It's really getting hot out here.

915
01:14:28,328 --> 01:14:31,244
是啊 变得好热
Yeah. Yeah, it is getting hot, Art.

916
01:14:31,330 --> 01:14:35,624
你怎么不挖个自己的洞?
Why don't you dig one of your own holes, huh?

917
01:14:35,709 --> 01:14:39,458
我只是在检查这个 而且... 无线电... 我在监督
I was just checking this one. Besides, the radio... I was monitoring...

918
01:14:39,546 --> 01:14:43,758
事情远比我们想得还棘手
This is turning out to be a lot more work than we thought it was gonna be.

919
01:14:43,842 --> 01:14:47,710
我们进屋吧 里面应该比较凉快
Why don't we check the house? It's probably a lot cooler in there.

920
01:14:47,805 --> 01:14:50,425
好主意 让我们试试屋子
That's a good idea.Let's try the house.

921
01:14:50,515 --> 01:14:53,184
从地下室开始
We'll start in the basement.

922
01:14:53,268 --> 01:14:57,597
我们从地下室开始 然后一路往上
We'll start in the basement and just work our way up.

923
01:14:57,689 --> 01:15:00,808
雷 我想我们在后院找不到东西的原因
<i>Ray, I'm thinking the reason we didn't find anything in the backyard...</i>

924
01:15:00,900 --> 01:15:03,460
是因为他们可能没有把尸体埋在后院 
<i>is because they probably weren't burying anybody in the backyard.</i>

925
01:15:03,528 --> 01:15:07,228
他们把尸体挖起来埋在地下室
<i>They were digging bodies up and they probably buried them in the basement.</i>

926
01:15:07,323 --> 01:15:09,565
只是可能而已 阿特
<i>That's a possibility, Art.</i>

927
01:15:09,659 --> 01:15:13,406
我们从厨房开始吧 那里可能有些冰啤酒
<i>I say we start in the kitchen. They probably got some cold beer in there.</i>

928
01:15:13,495 --> 01:15:17,078
或是德国蒜肠什么的 我饿死了
<i>Or some knockwurst or something. I'm starving.</i>

929
01:15:17,165 --> 01:15:20,083
门锁了
It's locked.

930
01:15:20,168 --> 01:15:22,375
把信用卡给我 - 
Hey, give me a credit card. 

931
01:15:40,146 --> 01:15:44,938
- 你从哪里学的? - 我不知道怎么弄
- Where did you learn how to do that? - I don't know how to do this.

932
01:15:48,279 --> 01:15:50,899
反正是一张烂卡
Ah, it's a shit store anyway.

933
01:15:55,952 --> 01:16:00,116
雷 你知道什么是 "擅闯空门" 吗?
Ray, do the words "breaking and entering" mean anything to you?

934
01:16:01,374 --> 01:16:07,247
伦斯菲先生 嘿!
<i>Hey, Mr Rumsfield! Hey, yo, man!</i>

935
01:16:07,339 --> 01:16:09,248
我想向你介绍我的朋友 
I wanted to introduce you to my friend.

936
01:16:09,341 --> 01:16:12,590
- 史帝夫昆兹 - 嘿 老兄
- This is Steve Kuntz. - Hey, dude.

937
01:16:12,676 --> 01:16:14,799
他今天下午过来看好戏
He's here to watch the show this afternoon.

938
01:16:14,887 --> 01:16:16,796
很好
Great.

940
01:17:00,305 --> 01:17:03,555
嘿 老兄 好戏什么时候开始?
Hey, man, when's the big unveiling, huh?

941
01:17:03,642 --> 01:17:09,348
- 我两小时候要去工作 - 嘿 老兄 滚开
- I gotta go to work in a couple hours. - Hey, man, piss off!

942
01:17:09,439 --> 01:17:12,854
把这个浑小子撵出你的院子
Get this lame-o out of your yard! 

943
01:17:12,942 --> 01:17:15,943
- 混小子 滚出我的院子 - 怎么搞的?
- Get out of my yard, lame-o! Hey! - What's his problem?

944
01:17:16,028 --> 01:17:18,187
滚出我的院子
<i>Get out of my yard!</i>

945
01:17:25,746 --> 01:17:28,368 
雷 看看暖炉的尺寸
<i>Ray, look at the size of this furnace.</i>

946
01:17:28,457 --> 01:17:30,947
这玩意一定有八十年历史了
This thing's got to be 80 years old.

947
01:17:31,042 --> 01:17:33,616
这种老房子一定很难取暖
These old places have got to be hell to heat.

948
01:17:33,712 --> 01:17:35,455
这栋房子没有那么大
<i>This house isn't that big.</i>

949
01:17:35,547 --> 01:17:39,710
要这种暖炉做什么?
What the hell does he need a furnace like this for?

950
01:17:41,678 --> 01:17:45,177
一定做过修改 导管是新的
I think there's been some modifications on this 'cause this conduit's brand new.

951
01:17:45,265 --> 01:17:47,886
它一直通到后面那里 然后从天花板的洞穿过去
It runs all the way back over there and up through a hole in the ceiling.

952
01:17:47,976 --> 01:17:50,466
有一些通到他们客厅
I saw some of that in their living room.

953
01:17:50,561 --> 01:17:53,230
家用暖炉的调温器
And a thermostat on a home furnace...

954
01:17:53,314 --> 01:17:56,018
需要到五千度吗?
Is that supposed to go to 5,000 degrees, do you think?

955
01:17:56,108 --> 01:17:57,982
那一定就是噪音的来源
It must be what all the noise was.

956
01:17:58,068 --> 01:18:00,028
看看这里装的东西
Look at all the stuff they put together down here.

957
01:18:00,070 --> 01:18:03,155
- 屋子里都是电池 - 少说有四十个
- They got this place wired with batteries. - There's got to be 40 of them.

958
01:18:03,240 --> 01:18:06,027
你看 这里有电
Look, we got power here.

959
01:18:23,343 --> 01:18:26,593
这不是普通的暖炉
This is no ordinary furnace.

960
01:18:33,268 --> 01:18:37,895
那是什么?
<i>What's that?</i>

961
01:18:44,488 --> 01:18:46,943
喂 伦斯菲!
<i>Yo, Rumsfield!</i>

962
01:18:52,662 --> 01:18:55,947
不得了!
<i>Awesome!</i>

963
01:18:56,040 --> 01:18:58,531
伦斯菲先生 你还好吗?
<i>Mr Rumsfield, are you okay?</i>

964
01:18:58,626 --> 01:19:01,295
- 我没事 - 帅呆了
- Yes, yes, I'm all right. - That was very cool, man.

965
01:19:02,588 --> 01:19:05,210
阿特 看
Art. Art, look.

966
01:19:05,299 --> 01:19:07,707
- 你看! 我找到了 - 松脱的土
- Look! I found it! - That's loose dirt.

967
01:19:07,802 --> 01:19:11,845
他们一定在暖炉里烧尸体
They must have burned his body up in the furnace...

968
01:19:11,930 --> 01:19:13,887
然后把他的骨头埋在这里
and then buried his bones right here.

969
01:19:13,974 --> 01:19:16,761
现在我们该怎么办?
What do we do now?

970
01:19:19,646 --> 01:19:21,555
我会告诉马克这里有个火葬场
I'll tell him that they built a crematorium down here.

971
01:19:21,648 --> 01:19:25,693
别告诉他 他会想跑下来看 等我们找到端倪再说
Don't tell him that. He'll just want to come down. Wait 'til we find something.

972
01:19:25,777 --> 01:19:28,398
雷 那可能要一整晚
Ray, that could take all night.

973
01:19:33,951 --> 01:19:38,577
伦斯菲先生 你们让整条街停电了
Mr Rumsfield, you guys managed to knock out the power in the entire block.

974
01:19:38,664 --> 01:19:40,989
搞不好整个城镇南端都停电
<i>Probably the whole south end of town.</i>

975
01:19:41,083 --> 01:19:43,040
瑞奇 给我闭嘴!
Ricky, shut up!

976
01:19:43,585 --> 01:19:46,586
我们要去麦当劳 
We're gonna make a run to McD's.

977
01:19:46,672 --> 01:19:49,459
- 你要来个麦当堡什么的吗? - 不行!
- You want a Quarterpounder or something? - Oh, no way!

978
01:19:49,550 --> 01:19:52,254
你们现在不能走 精彩好戏就要上场了
Hey, you guys can't go now. It's the best part.

979
01:19:52,343 --> 01:19:55,843
- 我打给送披萨的 - 好耶!
- I called the pizza dude. - All right!

980
01:20:25,751 --> 01:20:28,621
雷 我想我们可以放弃了 他们不可能埋的这么深 
<i>Ray, I think we can give up. They'd never bury him this deep.</i>

981
01:20:28,712 --> 01:20:34,334
除了我们之外 谁会一直挖到这团烂泥?
<i>Who, besides us, would dig this deep into this kind of sludge?</i>

982
01:20:34,425 --> 01:20:36,963
那是金属!
<i>That was metal!</i>

983
01:20:37,053 --> 01:20:39,508
你碰到地窖了!
That was metal! You hit a crypt!

984
01:20:39,597 --> 01:20:45,137
他们把他埋在地窖里! 我去拿喷灯! 我打给它
They buried him in a crypt! I'll get my blowtorch! I'll call it in!

985
01:20:45,227 --> 01:20:49,853
喂! 呃... 鹰眼 这是特遣部队一号
Hello! Hey, uh... Eagle Eye, this is Ground Force One.

986
01:20:49,940 --> 01:20:53,273
我们找到瓦特了 我马上来! 
We have found Walter! We found Walter! I'll be out in a minute!

987
01:20:53,360 --> 01:20:57,227
快挖! 太棒了! 我们找到他了
Dig there! Dig there! Oh, yes! We found him!

988
01:20:59,574 --> 01:21:01,816
我们逮到你了 鲁本
We caught you, Reub.

989
01:21:01,910 --> 01:21:05,326
你把我们当成傻子 可是你错了
You've been playing us for saps, but you were wrong.

990
01:21:48,454 --> 01:21:50,660
韦嘉纳先生! 阿特!
<i>Mr Weingartner! Art!</i>

991
01:21:50,747 --> 01:21:53,784
看那边! 现在就看!
Look! Look over there! Look! Right now!

992
01:22:01,049 --> 01:22:02,923
走开 走开 我自己来
Go on. Go on. I'll...

993
01:22:04,636 --> 01:22:06,545
瓦特!
<i>Walter!</i>

994
01:22:09,474 --> 01:22:12,427


995
01:22:12,518 --> 01:22:15,852
雷! 雷蒙!
Ray! Raymond!

996
01:22:16,814 --> 01:22:19,270
仔细听好 先生
<i>Listen up real carefully, mister.</i>

997
01:22:19,358 --> 01:22:21,647
我们碰到大麻烦了
We got a real problem.

998
01:22:21,736 --> 01:22:25,270
雷 你猜我看到谁了? 是瓦特
Hey, Ray, guess who's not in the basement? Walter!

999
01:22:25,364 --> 01:22:27,902
他回来了!
He's back! He's back!

1000
01:22:35,206 --> 01:22:38,907
柯罗佩回来了 还带着警察
<i>Klopeks! With coppers!</i>

1001
01:22:41,129 --> 01:22:43,038
拦住他们 我去找雷
Keep 'em busy. Keep 'em busy. I'll get Ray.

1002
01:22:43,131 --> 01:22:46,049
- 拦着他们! - 好的 没问题
<i>- Keep them busy! - All right, okay, all right!</i>

1003
01:22:46,134 --> 01:22:50,380
停车! 停啊! 别往前了!
Stop! Stop right there! Don't go any further!

1004
01:22:50,471 --> 01:22:54,053
我叫你停啊 停!
You're going! Stop!

1005
01:22:54,141 --> 01:22:57,759
警察先生 等等
Hey, Mr Officer, wait.

1006
01:22:57,853 --> 01:22:59,762
这些人在我爸妈家
There are these people in my parents' house...

1007
01:22:59,855 --> 01:23:01,812
把他们的食物吃光了!
and they're eating all their food!

1008
01:23:08,489 --> 01:23:10,397
雷 瓦特回来了
<i>Ray, Walter showed up!</i>

1009
01:23:10,490 --> 01:23:14,618
- 还有柯罗佩 我叫瑞奇去... - 我挖到瓦斯管了 快跑!
- The Klopeks! I got Ricky down there... - I hit the gas line! Run!

1010
01:23:14,702 --> 01:23:17,110
- 瓦斯! - 快跑!
- Gas!  - Run!

1011
01:23:17,205 --> 01:23:19,245
- 这里出了什么事? - 谢天谢地
<i>- What is the problem here? - Thank God you're here.</i>

1012
01:23:19,332 --> 01:23:22,203
- 没问题 警官 - 这不是警察的事
- No problem, sir. - This is not a police matter.

1013
01:23:22,293 --> 01:23:24,618
我们挖到瓦斯管 瓦斯管外洩!
<i>We hit a pipe! There's all kinds of gas!</i>

1014
01:23:24,712 --> 01:23:27,797
要爆炸了!
It's gonna blow!

1015
01:23:30,717 --> 01:23:34,501
- 棒呆了 - 瑞奇真知道怎么搞派对
- All right! - Ricky sure knows how to throw a party.

1016
01:24:05,001 --> 01:24:07,705
那是你的房子?
Was that your house?

1017
01:24:15,635 --> 01:24:17,592
雷
Ray.

1018
01:24:23,226 --> 01:24:25,682
那里有东西在动
Something is moving in there.

1019
01:25:01,679 --> 01:25:04,965
雷 你找到了 对吧?
Ray... Ray, you found it, right?

1020
01:25:05,058 --> 01:25:07,264
在爆炸之前你找到了 对吧?
Before it blew, you found it, right?

1021
01:25:07,352 --> 01:25:10,435
告诉我你找到了 对不对?
Hey, tell me you found it. You found it, right?

1022
01:25:10,520 --> 01:25:14,186
在一切爆炸之前你一定找到了
Before everything went off, you had to have found it.

1023
01:25:15,776 --> 01:25:18,314
先生 你有官司上身了
You got a lawsuit on your hands, mister.

1024
01:25:20,864 --> 01:25:24,565
天哪 怎么回事?
Oh, God, what's this?

1025
01:25:44,345 --> 01:25:50,172
请注意 远离路障
Your attention, please. Please stay behind the barricade.

1027
01:25:56,982 --> 01:26:00,232
请退后
You want to step back, please?

1028
01:26:00,318 --> 01:26:03,439
- 那是我家 - 抱歉 我得获得瓦斯公司批准
- That's my house. - Sorry. I've got to get the all clear from the gas company.

1029
01:26:03,530 --> 01:26:06,614
- 我可以批准 她住这里 - 我有问你吗?
- I can clear this. She lives here. - Did I ask you?

1030
01:26:06,700 --> 01:26:09,273
小姐 请后退 听到没?

1033
01:26:24,216 --> 01:26:29,555
- 亲爱的 他们把你怎么了? - 你剪了头发

1034
01:26:31,681 --> 01:26:33,590
我喜欢

1035
01:26:33,683 --> 01:26:36,518
警官 那栋房子埋了一具尸体

1036
01:26:36,603 --> 01:26:39,438
- 叫斯尼克的老人 对吧? - 对 坐在这里的这个老人...

1037
01:26:39,522 --> 01:26:42,013
- 被埋在那间房子里 - 小心点
- is buried in that house, Sherlock. - Watch it.

1038
01:26:42,108 --> 01:26:44,017
他到底跑哪去了?
Where was he anyway?

1039
01:26:44,110 --> 01:26:47,064
斯尼克先生今晚八点以前都在医院里
Mr Seznick was at the hospital 'til 8:00 this evening.

1040
01:26:47,155 --> 01:26:49,823
星期一晚上他心悸了
Monday night he had some heart palpitations.

1041
01:26:49,907 --> 01:26:54,403
他打电话给女儿和女婿 他们把他送到医院
He called his daughter and son-in-law, and they took him to the hospital.

1042
01:26:54,494 --> 01:26:57,994
那假发呢? 他们在房子里找到假发
What about the wig? They found a wig in this house.

1043
01:26:58,081 --> 01:27:00,288
- 他的假发 - 柯罗佩帮他收信
- His wig. - The Klopeks were picking up his mail.

1044
01:27:00,375 --> 01:27:04,836
医生可能把假发跟报纸及信件混在一起了
The doctor somehow got that wig mixed up with the newspapers and letters.

1045
01:27:04,922 --> 01:27:08,172
医生? 你真相信他是医生?
"Doctor"? You don't believe that this guy's a real doctor, do you?

1046
01:27:08,258 --> 01:27:10,582
对 我相信他是医生
Yes, I do believe he's a doctor.

1047
01:27:10,676 --> 01:27:14,010
事实上 他是一位受人尊敬的病理学家
In fact, he's a very well-respected pathologist, my friend.

1048
01:27:14,096 --> 01:27:18,094
你没有让他在那场爆炸丧生算你走运了
I'd say that you are damn lucky you didn't kill him in that blast.

1049
01:27:18,184 --> 01:27:22,051
是阿 谢天谢地
Oh, yeah, I thank my lucky stars.

1050
01:27:22,146 --> 01:27:26,938
- 好好照顾这个煳涂蛋 - 老兄 你的车抱歉了
- Take care of this nitwit. - Sorry about your car, man.

1051
01:27:27,026 --> 01:27:31,189
破坏私人财产 破坏公共财产
<i>Destruction of private property. Destruction of public property.</i>

1052
01:27:31,279 --> 01:27:34,364
三起刑事侵入罪
Three counts of criminal trespassing.

1053
01:27:34,449 --> 01:27:39,194
骚扰 攻击 破坏
Harassment, assault, vandalism.

1054
01:27:39,287 --> 01:27:41,695
那个老人还说他收到勒赎信
And that poor old man claims he's got a ransom note...

1055
01:27:41,790 --> 01:27:44,245
说你绑架他的狗
that says you kidnapped his dog!

1056
01:27:46,628 --> 01:27:49,083
你听得见吗 彼得森先生?
Do you hear me okay, Mr Peterson?

1057
01:27:51,715 --> 01:27:55,843
我真的喜欢你的发型
I really do like your hair, honey.

1058
01:27:55,928 --> 01:27:57,967
这不会改变事实
<i>You know, this doesn't change a thing.</i>

1059
01:27:58,055 --> 01:28:00,890
他们以为没事了 但可不是这样
They may think it does. They may think they're off the hook, but they're not.

1060
01:28:00,975 --> 01:28:03,596
他们有事 对吧? 告诉他们
No, they're not. Are they, Ray? Go ahead, tell 'em.

1061
01:28:03,686 --> 01:28:05,974
我们掌握了他们犯罪的证据
We got the goods on 'em, don't we?

1062
01:28:06,063 --> 01:28:08,221
哪一天他们去挖那个院子
Someday they're gonna dig up the back of that yard...

1063
01:28:08,315 --> 01:28:10,770
会发现股骨之外的整块残骸
and they're gonna find the rest of that skeleton to go with that femur.

1064
01:28:10,858 --> 01:28:15,070
- 可能不是瓦特 但... - 闭嘴 阿特!
- It might not be Walter, but... - Shut up, Art! Shut up!

1065
01:28:15,154 --> 01:28:18,654
天啊 你还不知道要罢手
God, you don't know when to quit, do you?

1066
01:28:18,741 --> 01:28:21,612
看看我!
Look at me!

1067
01:28:21,703 --> 01:28:24,372
都是因为你 我去掉半条命
I'm a shell of a man because of you, Art.

1068
01:28:24,455 --> 01:28:27,706
- 好了 - 士兵!
- Now, now... - Soldiers!

1069
01:28:27,792 --> 01:28:30,709
你别再去烦他们了!
You leave 'em alone! Get off their case already!

1070
01:28:30,794 --> 01:28:35,207
他们又没有对我们怎么样
They didn't do anything to us. They didn't do anything to us!

1071
01:28:35,299 --> 01:28:38,465
好吧 他们是不一样 他们独来独往
All right, so they're different! So they keep to themselves!

1072
01:28:38,552 --> 01:28:42,087
你能怪他们吗? 隔壁邻居闯进他们家里
Can you blame them? They live next door to people who break into their house...

1073
01:28:42,180 --> 01:28:44,850
在他们出门时把房子烧掉了
and burn it down while they're gone for the day.

1074
01:28:46,268 --> 01:28:49,850
还记得你说住在郊区的人吗?
Remember what you were saying about people in the 'burbs?

1075
01:28:49,937 --> 01:28:51,846
像史奇普的人
People like Skip?

1076
01:28:51,939 --> 01:28:57,645
锄了八百次的草后突然变了样
People who mow their lawn for the 800th time and then snap?

1077
01:28:57,737 --> 01:29:00,903
那就是我们! 不是他们!
Well, that's us! It's not them! That's us!

1078
01:29:00,990 --> 01:29:05,735
是我们跳过篱笆 偷窥别人的窗户
We're the ones vaulting over fences and peeking in through people's windows!

1079
01:29:05,828 --> 01:29:10,288
是我们把垃圾扔到街上 是我们点的火
We're the ones throwing garbage in the street and lighting fires!

1080
01:29:10,373 --> 01:29:13,160
是我们自己疑神疑鬼
We're the ones who are acting suspicious and paranoid, Art!

1081
01:29:13,251 --> 01:29:17,628
我们才是疯子! 不是他们!
We're the lunatics! Us! It's not them!

1082
01:29:19,215 --> 01:29:21,504
是我们
It's us.

1083
01:29:24,179 --> 01:29:28,093
我不知道要怎么说
I don't know what to say.

1084
01:29:28,183 --> 01:29:30,091
你要我搬家吗?
What, do you want me to move?

1085
01:29:33,938 --> 01:29:36,808
- 我要杀了他! - 你疯了!
- I'm gonna kill him! - You're crazy!

1086
01:29:38,901 --> 01:29:41,143
- 退后! -  住手!
- Back off! - Stop it! Stop it!

1087
01:29:41,237 --> 01:29:44,652
分开!
Break it up!

1088
01:29:44,740 --> 01:29:47,776
- 住手! - 我不管! 我被炸到了!
- Stop it! Stop it! - I don't care! I've been blown up!

1089
01:29:47,868 --> 01:29:50,026
带我去医院!
Take me to the hospital!

1090
01:29:50,119 --> 01:29:52,610
带我去医院 我不舒服
Take me to a hospital. I'm sick.

1091
01:29:52,705 --> 01:29:58,376
我的眼睛很痛
My eye hurts.

1092
01:30:06,719 --> 01:30:11,635
亲爱的 我会找出他们送你去哪家医院
Honey? I'll just find out what hospital they're taking you to...

1094
01:30:11,723 --> 01:30:15,507
然后我随后就到 
and then I'll... follow right along.

1095
01:30:15,602 --> 01:30:17,595
-好吗? - 好的
<i>- Okay? - Okay, honey.</i>

1096
01:30:18,897 --> 01:30:21,435
- 你还好吧? 我很好 卡罗
- You okay? - Yeah, I'm fine, Carol.

1097
01:30:31,075 --> 01:30:34,776
混小子 离开我的车
Okay, hepcats, get off my car!

1098
01:30:34,870 --> 01:30:37,540
老兄 你应该待久一点
Dude, you should hang out a little bit.

1099
01:30:37,623 --> 01:30:40,624
送披萨的马上就来了
We've got the pizza dude coming.

1100
01:30:40,710 --> 01:30:43,414
你这个白痴 呆子
You imbecile! You sub-moron, you!

1101
01:30:44,005 --> 01:30:48,216
是谁?
<i>Who's that?</i>

1102
01:30:49,677 --> 01:30:54,919
柯罗佩医生 很抱歉
Oh, Dr Klopek, I'm so sorry.

1103
01:30:55,015 --> 01:30:57,553
柯罗佩医生 等我出狱后
You know, Dr Klopek, when I get out of prison...

1104
01:30:57,642 --> 01:31:00,727
我会帮你重盖新房子
I'm gonna help you rebuild your house.

1105
01:31:00,812 --> 01:31:04,311
我甚至会亲手盖一部分 我有工具
I'll even do some of the work myself. I have the tools.

1106
01:31:04,399 --> 01:31:07,733
卡罗父亲刚送给我一套新工具
Carol's father just gave me a brand new set of tools.

1107
01:31:07,819 --> 01:31:12,195
我看起来像白痴吗 彼德森先生
Do I look like an idiot, Mr Peterson?

1108
01:31:12,281 --> 01:31:14,190
不像
No.

1109
01:31:14,283 --> 01:31:18,328
你把我当成傻子吗?
Do you take me for an imbecile?

1110
01:31:18,412 --> 01:31:20,321
没有
No.

1111
01:31:20,414 --> 01:31:24,957
你骗得了别人
You may have fooled the others, Mr Peterson...

1112
01:31:25,044 --> 01:31:27,036
可是骗不了我
but you don't fool me.

1113
01:31:28,464 --> 01:31:30,621
我骗了别人?
Uh, I fooled the others?

1114
01:31:30,715 --> 01:31:33,965
- 可是你骗不了我 - 我骗不了你?
<i>- But you don't fool me. - I don't?</i>

1115
01:31:34,052 --> 01:31:37,006
对 你骗不了
No, you don't.

1116
01:31:37,096 --> 01:31:39,469
我不懂你的意思
Am I missing something, Doctor?

1117
01:31:39,557 --> 01:31:44,682
少装了 彼德森先生 你在我的地下室
Come now, Mr Peterson. You were in my basement.

1118
01:31:44,771 --> 01:31:49,646
你当然看了暖炉里面
Surely, you looked in the furnace.

1119
01:31:49,733 --> 01:31:54,027
我看到了暖炉 医生
I saw your furnace, Doctor...

1120
01:31:54,112 --> 01:31:58,774
可是我认为暖炉是自家的事
but I figured a man's furnace is his own business.

1121
01:31:59,868 --> 01:32:03,700
你看到一个骷髅头了 对吧?
You saw one of my skulls, didn't you?

1122
01:32:03,789 --> 01:32:06,873
我知道你有
Oh, yes. I know you did.

1123
01:32:07,876 --> 01:32:11,493
它属于你的邻居
It belonged to a neighbour of yours.

1124
01:32:11,587 --> 01:32:15,799
名叫纳普斯
The name was Knapp.

1125
01:32:15,883 --> 01:32:19,086
我们的房子是从他们那来的
We took the house from them.

1126
01:32:19,178 --> 01:32:23,887
我像他们出价买房子 可是你知道老人是什么样子
I offered to buy it, but you know how old people are.

1127
01:32:23,975 --> 01:32:27,972
他们恋旧 捨不得
They grow so attached to things.

1128
01:32:28,062 --> 01:32:30,469
柯罗佩医生 我忘了皮夹
Uh, you know, Dr Klopek, I think I forgot my wallet.

1129
01:32:30,564 --> 01:32:35,309
我让你留着股骨
I let you keep the femur.

1130
01:32:35,402 --> 01:32:39,898
可是骷髅头要还我
Now, now, I want my skull.

1131
01:32:39,990 --> 01:32:43,822
也许 我应该拿你的
Or, perhaps, I might just take yours.

1132
01:32:43,910 --> 01:32:45,654
汉斯

1134
01:33:16,816 --> 01:33:18,939
送披萨的!

1135
01:33:25,617 --> 01:33:27,526
干得好!

1136
01:33:37,920 --> 01:33:41,502
真够瞧

1137
01:33:46,929 --> 01:33:50,593
公民逮捕!

1138
01:33:52,099 --> 01:33:56,311
我 雷彼德森 因为你企图谋杀

1139
01:33:56,395 --> 01:33:58,471
我以公民的身分逮捕你
for my attempted murder!

1140
01:33:58,564 --> 01:34:00,473
这个人不知道自己在说什么
The man doesn't know what he's talking about.

1141
01:34:00,566 --> 01:34:03,022
- 公民逮捕 - 雷
- Citizen's arrest. Citizen's arrest. - Oh, Ray.

1142
01:34:03,110 --> 01:34:05,981
别惹我 卡罗 他承认他们杀了纳普斯一家人
Don't start with me, Carol. The man confessed. They murdered the Knapps.

1143
01:34:06,072 --> 01:34:08,064
- 他精神错乱 - 嘿 福尔摩斯
<i>- He's demented. - Hey, Sherlock.</i>

1144
01:34:08,157 --> 01:34:10,730
叫柯罗佩告诉你 他们把尸体埋在哪里
<i>Get the Klopeks to tell you where they buried the stiffs.</i>

1145
01:34:10,825 --> 01:34:13,862
你拿不出尸体 你没有证据
<i>You don't have a stiff. You don't have any evidence.</i>

1146
01:34:13,954 --> 01:34:15,863
现在有证据了
You do now.

1147
01:34:27,008 --> 01:34:28,965
这是你的车吗 柯罗佩医生?
This your vehicle, Dr Klopek?

1148
01:34:33,013 --> 01:34:35,587
医生 我们走吧
<i>Let's go, Doc.</i>

1149
01:34:35,683 --> 01:34:40,309
嘿! 小木偶!
Hey! Pinocchio!

1150
01:34:40,396 --> 01:34:42,353
你要去哪里?
Where are you going?

1151
01:34:46,986 --> 01:34:49,109
逮到你了!
Gotcha!

